Suggests: wpctl
Description: Modern audio management application for Linux
 Linux Audio Manager is a GTK4 application for managing audio devices and
 volume routing on Linux systems using PipeWire.
 .
 Features:
  * Unified volume control for system, applications, and devices
  * Real-time audio topology visualization
  * Manual and automatic stream routing
  * Multi-device simultaneous playback
  * Persistent configuration and profiles
  * System tray quick access
